    </p>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-prime-gold text-prime-blue px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-opacity-80">Try PrimeFlux-Ai</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
